_sText:
Dustish map with dungeonish elements. Many thanks to 4izza for helping me out, being a great teacher, and assisting in pointing out/fixing several errors and leaks. Also thanks to CJC0008 for inspiring me to make this map, and for beta testing.

There's also a hidden room to those of you can find it...assuming you don't cheat and just noclip to it.

Known Issues:
-Some minute creases in parts of walls and around ramps, unsure of how to fix.
-Lighting error on the rock under the arch.
-Button that opens the hidden room door is visible on the other side of the wall momentarily.

PM if you find anything else, and be sure to tell me your thoughts.
